Had several issues during the stay:
- one day we had to wait more than 1h (and make 4 calls to front-desk) to receive blankets in the room;
- on one day housekeeping was not done by 5PM - so we came back to the room and had to call and wait 15min for them to show-up;
- one night the fire alarm went off at 3AM, we walked down the stairs for 22 floors and when arrived at the lobby one staff member just said "All good, you can go back up" - without any explanation or apologies;
I've stayed 4 nights in total, and had 3 issues in 3 different days.
